IT seems criminals in Mzansi are not afraid of anything anymore. A video showing a motorist being robbed on a highway in broad daylight has emerged on social media. It seems the motorists was forced to stop before the thugs took his belongings from his car. It is not yet clear what was taken from the car. The incident occurred on Xavier off-ramp towards Alberton. The video has angered a lot of people om social media.  